title: Dance Academy - Season 3 Episodes 1-3
description:
Dance Academy is an Australian teen-oriented television drama of students at the National Academy of Dance. It's told mainly from the perspective of Tara Webster, a new student.

Series two saw Tara return to the Academy for her second year with the hope of representing Australia in an international ballet competition, the Prix de Fonteyn. 

Series three sees the characters as seniors at the Academy, competing for a contract with the dance company.

Dance Academy series three started airing on ABC3 on 8 July 2013.
